<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Kwak%27wala&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Bibliography">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Bibliography">Bibliography</span></h2>
